    <item>
      <title>I do not need to go through it again</title>
      <link>https://GIGKOMUSIC.github.io/posts/00001-i_do_not_want_to_go_through_it_again/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>GIGKOMUSIC@gmail.com (GIGKO)</author>
      <guid>https://GIGKOMUSIC.github.io/posts/00001-i_do_not_want_to_go_through_it_again/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;If I had a chance to lead a new life in my high school time, what would I do? Such a question came to me today when I was playing Persona 4 Golden and reading a detective story called &amp;ldquo;体育館の殺人&amp;rdquo; by 青崎有吾.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
